window.bookSummaryJSON = "One Wedding. Two Families. Unlimited Chaos. Is Las Vegas family friendly or Sin City? Regan Harris is about to find out. Regan wants life to return to normal after her experiences in Chicago. Unfortunately, Vegas has other ideas. Surrounded by her family and friends, and with Gray by her side, Regan manages to squeeze in wedding plans, salon mishaps, bombs, and one missing person case. Here and Gone is the second book in Kelly Wood’s Regan Harris Romantic Mystery Series. If you like Janet Evanovich, Fern Michaels, and Nora Roberts, then you’ll love a series that combines all of their best traits in a humorous, light-hearted, romantic mystery. Buy now to follow Regan as she maneuvers through life, love, and mystery!"; 
